        <h2>The Ceremony</h2>

        <p>
            Our ceremony will be held a short 10 minute drive from the reception venue, at the Lightning Lakes day use area. See a map <a href="./accomodations#venue-map">here</a>.
        </p>

        <p>
            The ceremony will be outside, a very short walk from the parking lot in a grassy field so please come prepared.
        </p>
        
