        <p>
            After the ceremony, the bride and groom will sneak away for a couple moments to take some pictures with close family. Please take this time to head back down to the resort, take a nap, have a coffee, put on your dancing shoes, and prepare for a night of celebration.
        </p>

        <p>
            Join us for a cocktail, chat, and visit any time after 4pm in the Alpine Room next to the Manning Park Lodge.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

